---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';

const title = 'fun clicker | Privacy Policy';
const lastUpdated = '2026-02-09';
---

<SiteLayout
  title={title}
  description="How FunClicker.click collects, uses, and protects information, including advertising and cookies."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy"
>
  <section class="space-y-8 border-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium leading-loose text-gray-700">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how FunClicker.click (&quot;we&quot;, &quot;us&quot;, or &quot;our&quot;) collects, uses, and shares
        information when you visit our website (the &quot;Service&quot;).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong>Information you provide:</strong> if you contact us, we may receive your name, email address, and the
          content of your message.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> we may collect basic usage data such as pages viewed,
          approximate location (derived from IP), device/browser type, and referral source.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
      <p>
        We may use cookies, local storage, and similar technologies to operate the site, understand usage, and support
        advertising. You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling certain cookies may affect site
        functionality.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Advertising (Google AdSense)</h2>
      <p>
        We may use third-party advertising services such as Google AdSense. These services may use cookies and/or device
        identifiers to serve ads based on your visit to this and other websites.
      </p>
      <p>
        Google and its partners may serve ads using advertising cookies. You can learn more about Google&apos;s advertising
        practices and opt-out options by visiting Google&apos;s policies and ad settings pages.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>To provide and maintain the Service.</li>
        <li>To respond to inquiries and messages.</li>
        <li>To monitor and improve site performance and content.</li>
        <li>To detect, prevent, and address technical issues, abuse, or security incidents.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Sharing of Information</h2>
      <p>
        We may share information with service providers that help us operate the site (for example, hosting, analytics,
        and advertising partners). We may also disclose information if required by law or to protect the rights and
        safety of our users and the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain information only as long as necessary for the purposes described in this policy, unless a longer
        retention period is required or permitted by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The Service is not directed to children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information to
        us, please contact us and we will take appropriate steps to delete it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Your Choices</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Browser controls to block or delete cookies.</li>
        <li>Opt-out options provided by advertising partners, where available.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at
        <a class="underline font-black text-black" href="mailto:contact@funclicker.click">contact@funclicker.click</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
